{"id":156574,"type":6,"name":"Prometheus","name_cn":"普罗米修斯","date":"2012-06-08","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/1f/f4/156574_MaLPc.jpg","rating":{"rank":1523,"total":104,"count":{"1":0,"2":1,"3":0,"4":3,"5":4,"6":24,"7":36,"8":24,"9":7,"10":5},"score":7.1},"summary":"　　21世纪末，人类的科技水平已高度发达，克隆人技术和宇宙航行早已实现，不再是梦想。与此同时，许多科学家仍孜孜不倦追索着人类起源的秘密与真相。通过对许多古老文明的考察与对比，科学家伊丽莎白·肖（Noomi Rapace 饰）和查理·赫洛维（Logan Marshall-Green 饰）发现，人类可能是来自一个遥远星系的外星人创造的。在Weyland公司资助下，他们乘坐维克丝（查理兹·塞隆 Charlize Theron 饰）所掌管的宇宙飞船普罗米修斯号前往那颗未知的星球。\r\n　　经过对当地的考察，地球人的设想成功得到印证。可是他们贸然探查“神的秘密”的行为，也将自己引入万劫不复的深渊…… ","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>普罗米修斯</li><li><span>导演: </span><a href=\"/person/33659\" rel=\"v:directedBy\">Ridley Scott</a></li><li><span>制片人/制作人: </span>David Giler、Walter Hill、<a href=\"/person/33659\">Ridley Scott</a></li><li><span>主演: </span>Noomi Rapace、<a href=\"/person/35907\">Michael Fassbender</a></li><li><span>配角: </span>Charlize Theron、<a href=\"/person/56350\">Idris Elba</a>、Guy Pearce、Logan Marshall-Green、Sean Harris、Benedict Wong、Patrick Wilson</li><li><span>出品: </span><a href=\"/person/6818\">20th Century Fox</a></li><li><span>集数: </span>1</li><li><span>开始: </span>2012-06-08(美国)/2012-09-02(中国大陆)</li><li><span>类型: </span>动作 / 科幻 / 惊悚 / 恐怖</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>美国 / 英国</li><li><span>语言: </span>英语 / 苏格兰盖尔语</li><li><span>imdb_id: </span>tt1446714</li><li><span>片长: </span>124分钟</li><li><span>编剧: </span>Jon Spaihts、Damon Lindelof</li><li><span>制作: </span>Scott Free Productions、Brandywine Dune Entertainment</li>","collection":{"on_hold":0,"dropped":1,"wish":6,"collect":153,"doing":0},"tags":[{"name":"电影","count":24},{"name":"科幻","count":17},{"name":"异形","count":14},{"name":"欧美","count":10},{"name":"惊悚","count":9},{"name":"重口","count":9},{"name":"2012","count":8},{"name":"美国","count":5},{"name":"欧美电影","count":5},{"name":"2012年","count":3},{"name":"太空歌剧","count":2},{"name":"恐怖","count":1},{"name":"映画","count":1},{"name":"美剧","count":1},{"name":"","count":""}],"eps":[{"id":955255,"url":